commit.message: Chanage more skips. Turns out nondaemon still broken with eventlet. Force the virtualenv in wsgi config.
Skip this on pypy-gevent-cover (something is broken really bad, don't care).
Avoid some pytest bugs during regular CI.
Fix regression on setting process name. Drop support for py3.4 cause it don't have bytes % formatting.
Don't use encodings. Should be safe as input is from a controled place. Fixes not fully understood issue in #51.

commit.message:
socket timeout when accepting client connection

`socket.setdefaulttimeout()` would impact `socket.accept()` and in that case manhole thread shouldn't die.
